        <updateDate>2021-10-29T17:22:53Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Improving National Safety by Updating the Required Amount of Insurance Needed by Commercial Motor Vehicles per Event Act of 2021 or the</strong> <strong>INSURANCE Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill increases the minimum level of insurance required for motor carriers transporting property.</p> <p>The Department of Transportation must adjust the minimum insurance requirement every five years to account for inflation relating to medical care.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
